div.div: The fourth season of Overlord. E-Rantel, the capital city of the newly established Sorcerer Kingdom, suffers from a dire shortage of goods. Once a prosperous city known for its trade, it now faces a crisis due to its cautionor even fearof its king, Ainz Ooal Gown. To make amends, Ainz sends Albedo to the city as a diplomatic envoy. Meanwhile, the cardinals of the Slane Theocracy discuss how to retaliate against Ainz after his attack crippled the Re-Estize Kingdom's army, plotting for the Baharuth Empire to take over the Sorcerer Kingdom. However, when Emperor Jircniv Rune Farlord El Nix arranges a meeting with the Theocracy's messengers at a colosseum, he is confronted by none other than Ainz himself. With their secret gathering now out in the open, the emperor and his guests learn that Ainz has challenged the Warrior King, the empire's greatest fighter, to a duel. With Ainz's motivations beyond his comprehension, Jircniv can do nothing but watch as humanity's future changes before his very eyes. (Source: MAL Rewrite)
Shingeki no Kyojin: The Final Season

Its been four years since the Scout Regiment reached the shoreline, and the world looks different now. Things are heating up as the fate of the Scout Regimentand the people of Paradisare determined at last. However, Eren is missing. Will he reappear before age-old tensions between Marleyans and Eldians result in the war of all wars?
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Ashita, Watashi wa Dareka no Kanojo

"One time a week, I will be the girlfriend of [someone]." A bitter love story depicting the realities of love between female college students who earn money on behalf of her and men attracted by her. The first volume is a young office worker who rents the protagonist snow as a fake girlfriend, and draws a distorted love pattern of sota and snow. A substitute girl who plays the customer and the woman of their ideals to the end... Is the distance between two people's mind really close?
<i>Nominated for the Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Web Manga Category.<i>

I'm Berlina Lacotte, 18 years old. I've reincarnated into a fantasy world while retaining the memories of my previous life. Though I'm now an orphan, I'm able to live a satisfiying life in the city making use of the memories of my previous life as well the special skill I was given. One day, I met my soulmate. One of those guys commonly known as, "the hero." The instant I picked him out from the crowd, I knew it was meant to be. This was my was soulmate. A romantic comedy where the heroine is the pursuer. Note: Includes a side story.
